							</p>
							<p>{{item.data.goods_name}}</p>
							<p>
								<span style="display: block;" v-for="attr in item.data.attr">{{attr.attrName}}：{{attr.attrValue}}</span>
							</p>
							<p>
								<span></span><br />
								<span>¥{{item.data.shop_price_1}}</span>
							</p>
							<p>
								<span class="reduce lFloat" @click="changeShoppingNum($event,1)">
